{"tid":113758,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★深入探討IT人的社會地位！！","createTime":"2017-02-09T08:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T12:08:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bb1f9ff6b765c14c895e171fcb1526c357d0e84b","tid":113758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"IT雖受到社會各階層的歡迎，但以IT為生的職業低層員工卻屬於「賤民」，地位在基層市民之下。雖然有些當紅的IT人，能夠擠身豪們，成為達官貴人的座上客，然而在世人的眼中，他們的人格仍然是低下的，因為IT是供人娛樂的「玩意兒」，IT人就是為人取樂的。<br />\n<br />\n看不起IT人並不僅僅是官員，市民也同樣視IT為最下賤的職業。普通人家如有人去做「IT」，都會被認為是有辱家人，是不肖子孫。凡做「IT」的人要被開除族籍，名字不能上族譜，死後不能葬入宗族墳地。因此，很多人從IT之後，隱姓埋名，幾十年不與家人來往，以免玷辱祖宗。"},{"pid":"4978f300a0270e79a194c53178ec82c02310e3e7","tid":113758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:45:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e7d971599318236bc10a3b6a9de3a054585cbc","tid":113758,"uid":30647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:46:12.000Z","msg":"不肖子孫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"829fb63ca66b08ac26d7d869e0d9a7b71e7a0852","tid":113758,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:46:22.000Z","msg":"IT人FG做左3年野買左新樓"},{"pid":"d186f64c46a1ba507119a8d84bdee4c3a9d19403","tid":113758,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T08:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IT人FG做左3年野買左新樓</blockquote><br />\nYou again<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b92436d7209403521d2ccb5bde8a095acd2416","tid":113758,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T10:44:54.000Z","msg":"IT人個影唔可以叠到其他人個影 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"h